"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-marathon-runner-elroy-gelant-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport  ByWesley Botton  Chief sports journalist  3 minute read  8 July 2024  11:21 am  Elroy Gelant will compete at his third Olympics in Paris next month.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999987973447289, \"rank\": 1.2026567731684833e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Grant Pitcher/Gallo Images  Elroy Gelant dreams of returning home with an Olympic medal, but the experienced distance runner is not getting ahead of himself in the build-up to the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gelant, a former national 5 000m record holder on the track, has had an awesome season on the road.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He set a marathon personal best of 2:08:56 in Seville in February and went on to win the national title in 2:09:32 in Durban in April, which was enough tosecure a spot in the men's 42.2km raceat the Olympics, where he will turn out alongside compatriotStephen Mokoka.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999984647379695, \"rank\": 1.5321082432168386e-06, \"text\": \"Seville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"score\": 0.9999999999583906, \"rank\": 4.156380482711275e-11, \"text\": \"Durban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old athlete also won the SA half-marathon title in Gqeberha last month, clocking 1:03:54 in cold and wet conditions, and he showcased his form again over the weekend bysetting a 10km personal bestof 27:47 at the Absa Run Your City race in Durban.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999997933173, \"rank\": 1.1316968673484235e-10, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gqeberha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"score\": 0.9999999999583906, \"rank\": 4.156380482711275e-11, \"text\": \"Durban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He credits the efforts of his coach, Jean Verster, and their training group in Potchefstroom for helping him find the best form of his career.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"score\": 0.9999998616569978, \"rank\": 1.3834302022538414e-07, \"text\": \"Potchefstroom\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Winter in Potchefstroom is really cold, but even if it's minus two degrees, every morning at 4.45am we are out,\\\" Gelant said.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"score\": 0.9999998616569978, \"rank\": 1.3834302022538414e-07, \"text\": \"Potchefstroom\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potchefstroom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not miss one day, even if we are sick, and I think that discipline and consistency has helped with my performances this year.\\\"\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gelant will compete at his third successive Olympics in the French capital, after finishing 13th in the 5 000m final at the Rio 2016 Games and taking 33rd place in the marathon in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8868296624245339, \"rank\": 0.12201437773187668, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9887481868850944, \"rank\": 0.011279713062483846, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And though he wants a medal in Paris, he says a top-15 finish will be sufficient in terms of his personal goals.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999987973447289, \"rank\": 1.2026567731684833e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I train in the mornings I think of a medal, and everything I do, I am thinking of a medal, but I need to be realistic,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me it will be really good if I can get in the top 15 and then work towards the World Championships (in Tokyo) next year.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9887481868850944, \"rank\": 0.011279713062483846, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a bit of a breakthrough year for me, but I also can not be in a hurry.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of these things take time.\\\"\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2139, \"end\": 2145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9924066316853122, \"rank\": 0.007578342097394535, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2215, \"end\": 2226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Download our app  Get the latest news and updates on Whatsapp  The latest news directly in your inbox  Support Local Journalism  2026 The Citizen.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2298, \"end\": 2306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Whatsapp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": []}]}"